Such a fun game. Purrfect if you want to play for a few days to finish the main story. But has loads of extra play with interesting skillful combat and and plenty of NG+ options

My only gripe, and I would LOVE it if the developers implemented this;
Could they add a choice to swap the genders of the protagonaist and their sibling. It's just such an easy change that a lot of people really appreciate. Sisters want to save their brothers too
